thread.title: Jeppe Frderiksen

author: Jeppe Frderiksen
title: Jeppe Frderiksen
text: Arrived at Miami AirPort last Sunday. There was no driver at the AirPort. The hot line number for Flitways did not respond. After having waited an hour we took a yellow cab . Wrote to the help desk from the Hotel. Got a response after 2 days, claiming the driver had been busy.... I have today Thursday tried to call the help desk to ensure I'll be picked up as agreed tomorrow. An answering machine responded "the mailbox is full" ??? I have no trust to this company Needless to say I had prepaid everything. I clearly Recommend NOT to use this Company.
